author: Jorge Alonso
title: Wisconsin’s Zak Showalter Hits Miraculous Game-Tying 3-Pointer Then Does Discount Double Check With Aaron Rodgers Watching
text:
This is what legends are made of. 
During tonight’s Wisconsin-Florida sweet 16 game, Badgers guard Zak Showalter hit an amazing 3-pointer to tie the game with 2 seconds left. After the shot, Showalter pointed at Packers QB Aaron Rodgers who was sitting in the stands and the did Rodgers’ Discount Double Check celebration. 
Zak Showalter game-tying 3 and discount double check with Aaron Rodgers in the building pic.twitter.com/QtleUBe6CE 
— gifdsports (@gifdsports) March 25, 2017
